mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the 1st Annual Cajun Country Fete de Musique featuring Jack Greene, Jeannie Seely and the Renegades, Stonewall Jackson, Jackie Phelps, Merle Kilgore, Doug Jones, Bea Brown, Rick and Dianne, and Debbie and Wendy Falls at the Nicholls State University Stadium on March 12. Poster features metal photoplates of Jack Greene and Jeannie Seely, and of Stonewall Jackson. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/41553/
